INTRO                                             You see a petite woman of about thirty standing by the counter. "Welcome! Ye    hath arrived at the Sunray Pub & Inn."                                                                                  NAME                                              "Elsi. I runeth this place. The great Archmage himself, LEOMUND, comes here."                                                                                                                           JOB                                               "I run the inn and pub. My job is to serve FOOD to the customers, as well as    provide a place to SLEEP. Of course, I like to CHAT, too!"                                                              BYE                                               "My pleasure! Please patronize us again sometime! Fare thee well!"                                                                                                                                                                                        "Sorry, I know little about that."                                                                                                                                                                      NO                                                "Ah, perhaps thee wish to CHAT! I love to talk with visitors!"                                                                                                                                          YES                                               "Dost thous need FOOD, SLEEP, or just wish to CHAT?"                                                                                                                                                    SLEEP                                             "A bargain at only 5gp a night! Sweet dreams." She shows you to your room.                                                                                                                              FOOD                                              "We hath BANBAN fruit, GRAPES, MUTTON, FISH, BREAD, FOWL, OATMEAL, APPLES,      CHEESE and RICE. Which wouldst thou like today?"                                                                        BANBAN                                            "'Tis most fresh!"                                                                                                                                                                                      GRAPES                                            "Plump and juicy!"                                                                                                                                                                                      MUTTON                                            "Carved only this morning!"                                                                                                                                                                             FISH                                              "A fresh catch!"                                                                                                                                                                                        BREAD                                             "I bake it myself, I do!"                                                                                                                                                                               FOWL                                              "Excellent duck, caught only a few hours ago. Very fresh."                                                                                                                                              OATMEAL                                           "A good choice. It art very nutritious."                                                                                                                                                                APPLES                                            "Big, ripe and red! We import them from topside, you know!"                                                                                                                                             CHEESE                                            "Cheddar is what we make here. It's delicious!"                                                                                                                                                         RICE                                              "Pre-cooked and ready to eat, a very nutritious snack."                                                                                                                                                 FAKEOUT                                           FAKEOUT?                                                                                                                                                                                                LEOMUND                                           "He's a mighty one he is. If ye haven't spoken with him yet, thou wouldst be    wise to do so. He canst be very helpful!"                                                                               CHAT                                              "You might have met my sisters, KATY and MOLLY. We're all of the same family,   we are. Very much into the food business."                                                                              KATY                                              "She runs the BRIDGEway Inn & Pub down on the floor level."                                                                                                                                             MOLLY                                             "She runs the GREEN GROX Inn down on the floor level. Her and KATY are always   competing for business, Katy on the west side, Molly on the east!"                                                      BRIDGE                                            "'Tis a fine pub. But really, I thinketh we're a bit tastier up here!"                                                                                                                                  GREEN GROX                                        "A fair place. Watch out fer Molly, she loves to give handsome adventurers lots of samples of her brewery!" She winks at you.                                                                           